  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency argos-cli to v0.0.9",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli\">argos-cli</a> from <code>v^0.0.8</code> to <code>v0.0.9</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>argos-ci/argos-cli</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"009\">0.0.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/dcfdc9db21d2e8b2434bd0c95519dbae2a879558\"><code>dcfdc9d</code></a> v0.0.9</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/bdf9175fb6f450490ac4b8a8e73bd809ac57dbfc\"><code>bdf9175</code></a> core(js): run warn</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/14d866d4b8cc5e664796fd6b1dab6ec204cef82c\"><code>14d866d</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;16 from bokuweb/add-glob</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/15d89b33ef285188827d038ea148558f819208a4\"><code>15d89b3</code></a> fix:add glob to dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/8fb9c6b72140855a38a06a90f097591e7e3f02d9\"><code>8fb9c6b</code></a> core(npm): add more information</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/5b59b805014e1f0fe19002517f69fe22a85d5c80\"><code>5b59b80</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;14 from argos-ci/build-url</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/argos-ci/argos-cli/commit/48fce018b52f5856d05865031685b1ac5ae3c922\"><code>48fce01</code></a> feat(build): display the build url</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
